@startuml loop
title harness.loop — the phase graph (Navigator's transition table)

skinparam linetype ortho
hide empty description

[*] --> reason : start

state reason
state action
state observation

reason --> action : TOOLS_REQUESTED\n(Continue)
reason --> [*] : ANSWERED -> Halt\n(context.stopped)
action --> observation : ACTED\n(Continue)
observation --> reason : CONTINUE\n(Continue)
observation --> [*] : DENIED -> Halt\n(context.aborted)

note right of reason
  ReasonPhase: ask the ChatModel.
  ContextManager windows history;
  full context still folded in.
end note
note right of action
  ActionPhase / DelegatingActionPhase:
  run tools via ToolExecutor;
  principal also routes subagent calls.
end note
note right of observation
  ObservationPhase: Controller (hard deny)
  then ProgressTracker (nudge-once / stall).
end note

@enduml
